{"tid":2068931,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣陸委會下午將說明香港人道援助專案","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T07:49:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":106,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0647c05dd3d58272a8f030cc087b6270df5742","tid":2068931,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:48:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312894&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1312894%26csid%3D261_341&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=a7dc022f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312894&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣陸委會下午將說明香港人道援助專案<br />\n18.06.2020 12:26<br />\n在台灣，陸委會將會就「香港人道援助關懷行動專案」，下午4時舉行記者會說明，由主委陳明通主持。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會日前表示，已經大致完成援助港人的方案規劃，但隨著香港情勢快速變化和國際社會反應，需要再適度完善，否認是有疑慮或要叫停，待完成所有程序並核定後，會適時對外說明。"},{"pid":"f86377bc09e297e688d62ddebbc9b70df16123d2","tid":2068931,"uid":215876,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:17.000Z","msg":"救義士先！"},{"pid":"997a645bca8dfd390507865b16523ba90a2b1e87","tid":2068931,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f86377bc09e297e688d62ddebbc9b70df16123d2","tid":2068931,"uid":215876,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:17.000Z","msg":"救義士先！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:34.000Z","msg":"肯定啦"},{"pid":"fd7ac9d9c31f8ec9467ad3b421245089a9ce2c44","tid":2068931,"uid":307619,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068918</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"0c1cc15c5a78a6f613094fb0144df605bb4ca12e","tid":2068931,"uid":57674,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"真係等埋夏威夷派對先公佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cff79dfe1395b9677c6428f7014b3d68b0ccba","tid":2068931,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0c1cc15c5a78a6f613094fb0144df605bb4ca12e","tid":2068931,"uid":57674,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"真係等埋夏威夷派對先公佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"入直路啦<br />\n無彎轉"},{"pid":"c67858171b757640d0f1202dbf2181f3d46edf0e","tid":2068931,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747710527a8ac11464e7680d0eb983179